column16:
'desc': [u'

Offbeat Printed Men's Round Neck T-Shirt Price: Rs.385

Dress yourself in this stunning black T-shirt from Offbeat and make a dazzling style statement that becomes an envy of others. Designed to satiate the style needs of a modern man
column17:
this printed T-shirt is carefully made of 100 per cent cotton to assure you a comfy and refreshed feel. This single jersey knitted T-shirt is exclusively embossed with a rubber graphic print on the front which makes this understated piece unique and stylish. Bring a refreshing change to your daily wear collection by bringing home this half-sleeved T-shirt which comes with a round neck.

\r\n

\r\n\tSport a dashing look by teaming this Offbeat Round Neck T-shirt with a pair of dark colored jeans and casual leather shoes for a fresher\u2019s day at your college. Accessorize your casual look by putting on your favorite shades and a sling bag. Dedicatedly stressing on comfort and style
column18: Offbeat\u2019s innovative and fashionable casual T-shirts offer to give your personality a charismatic aura and an ultra-chic
